907
00:25:20,680 --> 00:25:21,080
Yeah.

908
00:25:21,080 --> 00:25:22,250
You two

909
00:25:22,280 --> 00:25:24,160
- Broken family.
- can figure it out.

910
00:25:24,780 --> 00:25:26,060
A broken butterfly.

911
