Not me.

919
00:25:37,300 --> 00:25:38,340
No.

920
00:25:38,340 --> 00:25:39,020
No, not me.

921
00:25:39,020 --> 00:25:40,020
Could you be...

922
00:25:42,660 --> 00:25:43,420
That's possible.

923
00:25:43,660 --> 00:25:44,340
Maybe Uncle Ke

924
00:25:44,340 --> 00:25:45,160
