I don't remember anything bad I did.

949
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:31,520
It was really uncomfortable.

950
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:34,560
This kind of role really...

951
00:26:34,560 --> 00:26:35,080
I...

952
00:26:35,800 --> 00:26:37,440
Before every shoot, I always...

953
00:26:37,460 --> 00:26:38,980
(Instilling confidence)

954
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:39,680
Yeah.

955
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:40,160
What's fun

956
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:41,200
