971
00:27:07,440 --> 00:27:09,400
After I saw the letter...

972
00:27:09,870 --> 00:27:10,260
Kid...

973
00:27:10,260 --> 00:27:10,920
Then I...

974
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:11,780
