992
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:32,280
Yeah. I knew.

993
00:27:32,280 --> 00:27:33,080
You knew?

994
00:27:33,080 --> 00:27:34,840
I couldn't tell at all.

995
00:27:34,840 --> 00:27:36,400
You're scary.

996
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:37,720
You're completely different from when I

997
