1001
00:27:41,800 --> 00:27:44,000
Honestly, you two are basically equal.

1002
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:44,980
(Evenly matched)

1003
00:27:45,090 --> 00:27:45,430
She...

1004
00:27:45,430 --> 00:27:46,090
Not you?

1005
00:27:46,090 --> 00:27:46,740
(Not you?)

1006
00:27:46,740 --> 00:27:47,380
