1013
00:27:54,340 --> 00:27:55,190
I didn't give it to her.

1014
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:56,620
You didn't?

1015
00:27:57,220 --> 00:27:58,540
I didn't give it to her.

1016
00:28:00,100 --> 00:28:02,100
