1026
00:28:14,100 --> 00:28:14,470
Yeah.

1027
00:28:14,470 --> 00:28:15,990
I'm in charge of the technical work.

1028
00:28:15,990 --> 00:28:17,060
Yeah.

1029
00:28:17,060 --> 00:28:18,970
Then that means...

1030
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:19,750
He.

1031
00:28:20,850 --> 00:28:21,650
Me?

1032
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:23,680
He's getting nervous.

1033
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:25,200
His expression...

1034
