1047
00:28:43,420 --> 00:28:44,700
Don't worry, darling.

1048
00:28:44,700 --> 00:28:45,780
I can explain everything.

1049
00:28:48,020 --> 00:28:48,900
I believe you.

1050
00:28:50,400 --> 00:28:50,920
Look

1051
