1067
00:29:14,420 --> 00:29:14,940
Even if I

1068
00:29:14,940 --> 00:29:15,900
had a secret with Aunty Pai,

1069
00:29:17,100 --> 00:29:18,660
what makes you say I killed An Er?

1070
00:29:18,660 --> 00:29:19,900
What does that have to do with him?

1071
00:29:22,800 --> 00:29:23,460
- So mad.
- Wen,

1072
00:29:24,500 --> 00:29:25,740
