1073
00:29:27,720 --> 00:29:29,360
Your sister's totally
into guys like him.

1074
00:29:30,880 --> 00:29:33,320
Ding is so pitiful.

1075
00:29:33,320 --> 00:29:34,440
From start to finish...

1076
00:29:34,800 --> 00:29:36,680
From start to finish,

1077
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:37,800
