1078
00:29:39,100 --> 00:29:40,020
Huan.

1079
00:29:40,020 --> 00:29:40,660
Okay.

1080
00:29:41,300 --> 00:29:41,860
Unlocked.

1081
00:29:41,860 --> 00:29:43,080
(Hubby King He)

1082
