That's so two-faced.

1083
00:29:46,500 --> 00:29:46,980
(So shocked)

1084
00:29:46,980 --> 00:29:48,540
I think you should explain this.

1085
00:29:48,540 --> 00:29:50,380
I think you should explain

1086
00:29:50,900 --> 00:29:51,490
