1088
00:29:53,900 --> 00:29:54,900
What does that mean?

1089
00:29:54,900 --> 00:29:55,620
(Also confused)

1090
00:29:55,620 --> 00:29:56,180
What?

1091
00:29:56,180 --> 00:29:58,460
It means the king among husbands.

1092
00:29:58,460 --> 00:29:59,740
(The top husband, Hubby King)

1093
00:29:59,760 --> 00:30:00,480
Wang He?

1094
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:04,040
Wang He.

1095
00:30:04,070 --> 00:30:06,060
What a shameless man.

1096
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:10,440
What right do you have
to call me shameless?

1097
00:30:10,800 --> 00:30:11,800
Who was the one who got drunk?

1098
00:30:12,280 --> 00:30:13,680
When I get a chance, I will.

1099
00:30:14,200 --> 00:30:15,280
