1105
00:30:20,740 --> 00:30:22,560
"Don't worry".

1106
00:30:23,120 --> 00:30:25,000
"I can totally handle her".

1107
00:30:27,380 --> 00:30:28,460
Wen!

1108
00:30:28,600 --> 00:30:29,160
So romantic.

1109
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:31,800
He Jiahuan and Pai's romance.

1110
00:30:32,060 --> 00:30:33,160
He takes turn

1111
00:30:33,160 --> 00:30:35,870
